---
/**
 * ai-agents · 0005 · Figure 9 — cost drivers stack + cost-vs-steps super-linear
 * curve. Verbatim from the source HTML.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 620 210"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Left: a stack of cost drivers. Right: a curve showing cost rising super-linearly with step count because history is re-sent each step"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <!-- drivers stack -->
            <text
                x="150"
                y="16"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#6b675f"
                letter-spacing=".05em">COST DRIVERS</text
            >
            <rect x="20" y="26" width="260" height="26" rx="5" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect><text x="30" y="43" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >input tokens &mdash; <tspan font-weight="700"
                    >whole history re-sent each step</tspan
                ></text
            >
            <rect x="20" y="56" width="260" height="26" rx="5" fill="#fbf3e6" stroke="#b07d18"
            ></rect><text x="30" y="73" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >output tokens &mdash; reasoning + tool args</text
            >
            <rect x="20" y="86" width="260" height="26" rx="5" fill="#fbf3e6" stroke="#b07d18"
            ></rect><text x="30" y="103" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >loop iterations &mdash; more steps, more calls</text
            >
            <rect x="20" y="116" width="260" height="26" rx="5" fill="#f3f7ec" stroke="#7a8a3f"
            ></rect><text x="30" y="133" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >tool / retrieval calls &mdash; APIs, vector search</text
            >
            <rect x="20" y="146" width="260" height="26" rx="5" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect><text x="30" y="163" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >multi-agent fan-out &mdash; <tspan font-weight="700">&times; N agents</tspan></text
            >
            <text x="150" y="190" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#9c968a"
                >model tier multiplies all of the above</text
            >
            <!-- curve -->
            <text
                x="460"
                y="16"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#6b675f"
                letter-spacing=".05em">COST vs STEPS</text
            >
            <line x1="330" y1="180" x2="600" y2="180" stroke="#6b675f" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
            <line x1="330" y1="180" x2="330" y2="30" stroke="#6b675f" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
            <text x="465" y="198" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >steps &#8594;</text
            >
            <text
                x="322"
                y="105"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="8.5"
                fill="#6b675f"
                transform="rotate(-90 322 105)">cumulative $</text
            >
            <!-- linear ref -->
            <line
                x1="330"
                y1="180"
                x2="595"
                y2="120"
                stroke="#bdb8b0"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                stroke-dasharray="4 3"></line>
            <text x="560" y="116" font-size="8" fill="#9c968a">linear (naive)</text>
            <!-- superlinear curve -->
            <path d="M330,180 Q500,168 560,60 T595,38" fill="none" stroke="#9a2417" stroke-width="2"
            ></path>
            <text x="520" y="52" font-size="8.5" font-weight="700" fill="#9a2417"
                >actual: re-sent</text
            >
            <text x="520" y="64" font-size="8.5" font-weight="700" fill="#9a2417"
                >history compounds</text
            >
            <!-- caching arrow -->
            <path
                d="M595,38 Q580,90 575,120"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-dasharray="3 2"
                marker-end="url(#arwG)"></path>
            <text x="540" y="150" font-size="8" fill="#2f5d3a">caching + compaction</text>
            <text x="540" y="161" font-size="8" fill="#2f5d3a">bend it back down</text>
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Each step re-sends the growing prefix, so a 30-step task isn't 30&times; one call &mdash;
        it's the sum of a growing context. Prompt caching and compaction flatten the curve;
        multi-agent steepens it.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
